          <head>
            <note type="contents-note">This manuscript contains: The Psalms, according to the Peshitta version, with a marginal division into ܗܘ̈ܠܠܐ and ܡܪ̈ܡܝܬܐ.; The Canticles.; Hymns and Prayers for various occasions.; Conciones, for several occasions.; Hymns addressed to the martyrs. In total, including sub-sections, this manuscript contains 36 items.</note>
            <listRelation type="Wright-BL-Taxonomy">
              <relation name="dcterms:type" ref="http://purl.org/dc/terms/type" active="https://bl.syriac.uk/ms/980" passive="#psalter">
                <desc>Psalters</desc>
              </relation>
            </listRelation>
          </head>
          <msContents>
