                <incipit xml:lang="syr">ܚܲܝܸܠ ܡܪܢ ܐܝ̈ܕܐ ܕܦܫ̣ܛܘ. ܘܫܩ̣ܠܘ ܩܘܕܫܐ ܠܚܘ̈ܣܝ ܚܘ̈ܒܐ.
                           ܏ܘܫ</incipit>
                <note>Forshall and Rosen are wrong in supposing (Catalogue, p. 13) that
                              <persName>Yazdīn</persName>, <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܙܕܝܢ</foreign>,
                           may be an error of the scribe for <persName>Yazīdād</persName>,
                           <foreign xml:lang="syr">ܝܙܝܕܕ</foreign>.</note>
              </msItem>
